# pdnd_eservice_descriptor_declared_attributes (Resource)

Manages declared attribute groups on a PDND E-Service Descriptor.

Attributes within a group are OR'd (consumer needs at least one from each group). Groups are AND'd (consumer must satisfy all groups).

